Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.89,0:03:14.36,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}有些麻烦呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.08,0:03:14.69,OPCN2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}（肯定）
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.69,0:03:16.05,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}兴趣相投
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.64,0:03:16.29,OPCN2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}（所以）
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.05,0:03:18.23,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}在看（着谁？就是你吧！）
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.23,0:03:22.63,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}只看着你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.57,0:03:22.63,OPCN2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}（这个美梦 咖啡杯之梦）
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.63,0:03:25.40,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}把梦之醴泉 饮干净吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.40,0:03:29.27,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}总是一蹦一蹦可能 追求着快乐
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.27,0:03:32.09,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}让活力再迸发出来点吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.47,0:03:35.05,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}聚在一起最好了！
