Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.91,0:23:14.15,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5}ラッダッダ 楽しいね
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.98,0:22:04.06,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5}淡淡春风轻轻拂过
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.22,0:22:06.51,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5}幽幽小径缓缓而行
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.04,0:22:09.63,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5}一如往日你的笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.84,0:22:12.55,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5}定能展现我眼前
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.82,0:22:16.83,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5}草莓帕妃虽然不错
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.02,0:22:19.43,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5}此刻却是咖啡拿铁的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.67,0:22:22.40,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5}加速的心跳不断更新
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.51,0:22:25.38,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5}是我每天的期待
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.23,0:22:29.07,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5}甜蜜蜜 酸溜溜
